{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was all kinds of entrances, all kinds of, of accommodations, you know, which, which was incredible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know whether now, at this time, it's open to the-- I, I don't think it's open anymore to-- open to the public.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this, this was an incredible, incredible, experience, you know, to, to be there at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I, I changed-- at that time, I, I called myself Arkadi, not Abraham, because they used to make-- tell jokes about Abraham and some-- you know, like, like satire, just very offensive.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know-- and that the Jews didn't like to fight, that they're always in the-- in the supply departments and that-- they were quite-- it was quite a strong anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in, in my case, I had also my-- the colonel that was in charge that I was working with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Biriuk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had his family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I, I was truthfully very close to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because at a later date, we used to have informants.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And most of the informants were extremely wealthy people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, we had a-- one of the informants was the head of the-- of the gramophone factory, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- another one was on the slaughterhouse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to come-- I used to have a motorcycle with a side wagon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I used to come in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to load all kinds of goods there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I used to take that to Alexanderplatz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a place where we used to sell this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I used to bring the, the, the proceeds to, to, to my-- to the commander and give it to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Which-- he would give me, in return, some share.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I used to be very, very straight with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he liked me very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
